These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, journalist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, ambient
1. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | journalist | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | folk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, scooter
1. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | ferret   | cat      |
| Transport   | car | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | country | jazz    |
| Transport     | tram | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, spy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, disco
1. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | spy |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
