.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | trance |
| Transport     | quad-bike   | ship    |

